narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Pretty chill. Just do a lot of research and write about your failings at the end.
Pick a good lab. You probably know the drill by now: research proposal, work in lab for many hours, presentation, final paper.
